data.description: This 5 bedroom 4.5 Bathroom 3 Car Garage 2 Story sits on a large fenced .39 acre lot with new in ground sprinkler system. This Integrity built home offers large open space concept anchored by large living room with stone gas fireplace, beautiful wood floors, large eat-in & formal dining areas, well-appointed kitchen with double ovens, upgraded gas range, tiled and stone backsplash, walk-in pantry, granite counters, granite breakfast island and custom cabinets. Enjoy outdoors by stepping onto the covered deck with ceiling fan or enjoy the evening by the firepit. Come see the large master suite with lit tiered ceiling, incredible owners bathroom with double bachelor height granite vanities, jetted tub & large walk-in closet. Enjoy movie night in the finished lower level or work out in the exercise area. This home has a 92% efficient furnace, tyvek wrapped insulation and low e windows.
